Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait across all process variants where it appears
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait when followed by Completed + Resolved compared to when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Resolved occurs

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants that include Completed + In Call versus variants that do not
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + In Call in cases where both activities occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Accepted + Wait when Completed + In Call occurs later in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Wait in variants ending with Completed + Closed after a Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait in cases that contain Completed + In Call versus cases that contain Completed + Resolved but not Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Time from Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Wait in process paths that eventually lead to Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait when preceded by Accepted + Assigned and followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100) that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Duration of Accepted + Wait compared to the duration of Accepted + Wait - User in variants that also contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Time between Accepted + Wait and the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress in traces that later execute Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait in cases originating from Brazil versus USA versus France when Completed + In Call is present
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Wait in the variant: Accepted + In Progress → Accepted + In Progress → Accepted + Wait → Accepted + In Progress → Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
